@startuml
actor User as U
participant "Python インタプリタ" as Py
participant "main.py" as Main
participant "screens/home.py" as Home
participant "Kivy Builder" as Builder
participant "TestApp" as App

U -> Py : main.py を実行
Py -> Main : main.py の読み込み開始
Main -> Home : from screens import HomeScreen
Home -> Builder : Builder.load_file("home_screen.kv")
Builder -> Builder : kvファイルを解析・登録
Builder --> Home : 登録完了
Home --> Main : HomeScreenクラス読み込み完了

Main -> App : TestApp() を生成
U -> App : run() 呼び出し
App -> App : build() 実行
App -> Builder : 登録済みkv情報を参照してUI構築
App -> App : on_start() 実行（UI描画済み）
@enduml
